WEBVTT

00:17.330 --> 00:21.528
Captions made possible by
HOME BOX OFFICE

00:21.530 --> 00:25.455
A Division of TIME WARNER
ENTERTAINMENT COMPANY, LP.

01:57.800 --> 01:59.791
OKAY, LET'S GO THEN !

01:59.800 --> 02:01.552
( dog barking )

02:01.560 --> 02:02.652
ARE YOU PACKED ?

02:02.660 --> 02:06.323
DON'T FORGET
THE DOG, HONEY.

02:08.860 --> 02:10.452
MICHAEL ?

02:10.460 --> 02:14.123
DON'T FORGET
THE DOG, HONEY.

02:15.600 --> 02:17.295
HOW ARE YOU FEELING ?

02:22.000 --> 02:24.127
HE'S NOT IN THE CAR,
IS HE ?

02:24.130 --> 02:25.927
WHY IS HE TALKING
ABOUT A DOG ?

02:25.930 --> 02:27.090
WHAT DOG ?

02:27.100 --> 02:29.227
WE HAD A DOG
IN BOULDER.

02:36.160 --> 02:37.491
WHAT IS THIS ?

02:37.500 --> 02:38.956
WE'RE IN THE HOSPITAL.

02:38.960 --> 02:41.258
YOU'RE SICK,
REMEMBER ?

02:41.260 --> 02:43.455
BUT YOU'RE GONNA
BE JUST FINE.

02:43.460 --> 02:47.123
RITA, LYING TO HIM DOESN'T
HELP ANYBODY BUT YOU.

02:52.530 --> 02:53.827
STOP IT.

02:53.830 --> 02:55.320
NURSE !

02:55.330 --> 02:56.797
IT'S OKAY
TO LET GO.

02:56.800 --> 02:57.653
NURSE !

02:57.660 --> 02:59.491
I'M GONNA BEAT IT.

02:59.500 --> 03:02.549
BUT MAYBE YOU CAN'T.

03:02.560 --> 03:04.198
YOU DON'T HAVE TO.

03:06.800 --> 03:08.529
WHY WOULD
YOU SAY THAT ?

03:08.530 --> 03:12.091
I DON'T WANT YOU
TO BE SCARED.

03:14.630 --> 03:16.723
I DON'T WANT TO DIE.

03:19.800 --> 03:21.449
I'M NOT GONNA DIE.

03:21.460 --> 03:26.159
THAT'S JUST YOUR BODY,
IT'S NOT YOU.

03:27.430 --> 03:29.853
THAT'S BULLSHIT, EILEEN.

03:32.130 --> 03:34.121
EXCUSE ME.

03:35.360 --> 03:36.452
HERE YOU GO.

03:36.460 --> 03:37.950
WE'RE GOING TO INCREASE
YOUR MORPHINE,

03:37.960 --> 03:39.689
ALRIGHT, MR. PIPER ?

03:53.860 --> 03:56.499
DO YOU SEE ?

03:58.360 --> 03:59.452
RITA ?

03:59.460 --> 04:01.428
ABOVE HIS HEAD ?

04:01.430 --> 04:03.398
THE LIGHT ?

04:03.400 --> 04:06.927
HE'S A GOOD BOY,
HE'S A GOOD BOY.

04:13.500 --> 04:16.628
( whistling )

04:18.430 --> 04:20.955
(flatlining sound )

04:26.560 --> 04:28.994
( dog barking )

04:34.230 --> 04:36.824
BE'I'I'ER HURRY UP,
WE'VE GOT MRS. PIPER AT 8:30.

04:36.830 --> 04:38.422
YEAH, I'LL BE
RIGHT THERE.

04:38.430 --> 04:41.024
WHATCHA DOIN', DAVE ?

04:41.030 --> 04:43.954
DOWNLOADING SOME PICS
FROM MANSLUTS-DOT-COM ?

04:43.960 --> 04:46.190
"LIVING WITH AVM".

04:46.200 --> 04:48.589
GREAT, DAVE, THAN KS.

04:48.600 --> 04:50.556
I JUST THOUGHT WE SHOULD
HAVE ALL THE INFORMATION.

04:50.560 --> 04:51.925
WELL, I HAVE ALL
THE INFORMATION.

04:51.930 --> 04:52.794
I DON'T THINK YOU DO.

04:52.800 --> 04:54.392
IF YOU DON'T
GET THIS TREATED,

04:54.400 --> 04:56.857
YOU COULD HAVE SEIZURES
WITH MUSCULAR TWITCHING,

04:56.860 --> 04:58.191
LOSS OF
VERBAL SKILLS...

04:58.200 --> 05:01.192
YOU COULD EVEN HAVE SOME KIND
OF HEMORRHAGE, AT SOME POINT.

05:01.200 --> 05:03.122
OR I COULD BE IN THE WRONG
AIRPLANE, AT SOME POINT.

05:03.130 --> 05:04.449
OR SO COULD YOU.

05:04.460 --> 05:06.428
ALRIGHT ?
C'MON.

05:14.630 --> 05:15.927
THE PARLIAMENT.

05:15.930 --> 05:17.625
IT'S VERY ELEGANT.

05:17.630 --> 05:18.528
YES,

05:18.530 --> 05:21.124
I LIKE IT.

05:22.300 --> 05:24.552
BUT MICHAEL
THINKS IT'S TACKY.

05:33.430 --> 05:35.091
THAT'S THE CLEVELAND.

05:35.100 --> 05:36.897
IT'S A MORE
AFFORDABLE CHOICE,

05:36.900 --> 05:38.925
BUT AS YOU CAN SEE,
IT'S NOT QUITE AS...

05:38.930 --> 05:40.397
GRACIOUS.

05:40.400 --> 05:41.924
REALLY, NO ?

05:41.930 --> 05:45.388
BUT IT'S JUST SO,
SORT OF, SELF-EFFACING...

05:46.730 --> 05:48.220
BUT WHY ?

05:48.230 --> 05:50.551
MRS. PIPER ?

05:50.560 --> 05:52.357
I'M SORRY, CAN YOU
EXCUSE ME FOR A MOMENT ?

05:52.360 --> 05:54.828
I CAN'T CARRY ON
TWO CONVERSATIONS AT ONCE.

05:56.330 --> 05:58.321
IT'S EXACTLY LIKE
THAT HORRIBLE IKEA COUCH

05:58.330 --> 06:00.628
YOUR MOTHER BOUGHT US !

06:05.530 --> 06:07.225
MICHAEL CLAIMS
TO LOVE THIS ONE.

06:07.230 --> 06:09.755
IN MY OPINION,
HE'S JUST TRYING TO DO

06:09.760 --> 06:11.921
WHAT HE THINKS
HIS MOTHER WANTS.

06:11.930 --> 06:13.295
WHICH IS TYPICAL,
REALLY.

06:13.300 --> 06:17.259
FINE, DENY IT,
WHY CHANGE NOW ?

06:17.260 --> 06:20.149
WOULD YOU LIKE
TO SIT DOWN FOR A MINUTE ?

06:20.160 --> 06:21.491
OH, I'M FINE.

06:21.500 --> 06:23.024
IT'S JUST,
MICHAEL'S HERE.

06:23.030 --> 06:25.089
HE DIDN'T WANT TO DEAL
WITH ANY OF THIS STUFF

06:25.100 --> 06:26.590
WHEN HE WAS ALIVE.

06:26.600 --> 06:28.625
YOU KNOW,
THE FUNERAL.

06:28.630 --> 06:30.393
NOW HE'S VERY
OPINIONATED.

06:30.400 --> 06:32.049
HUH.

06:32.060 --> 06:35.223
I'M A PSYCHIC,
SO, YOU KNOW...

06:35.230 --> 06:36.697
WOW.

06:36.700 --> 06:39.055
THAT MUST BE VERY
INTERESTING FOR YOU.

06:39.060 --> 06:42.154
IT'S JUST
MORE INFORMATION.

06:48.360 --> 06:50.828
THIS ROOM HAS A LOT
OF PAIN IN IT.

06:50.830 --> 06:52.627
WELL...

06:52.630 --> 06:55.121
YES.

06:56.700 --> 06:58.827
YOU HAVE A LOT
IN YOUR MIND.

06:58.830 --> 07:00.297
ON YOUR MIND, I MEAN.

07:00.300 --> 07:02.689
DON'T YOU ?

07:02.700 --> 07:05.089
YEAH, I GUESS SO.

07:05.100 --> 07:06.556
DON'T WORRY.

07:06.560 --> 07:09.620
IT'S OKAY,
ALRIGHT ?

07:09.630 --> 07:12.451
IT'S ALL
GONNA BE OKAY.

07:12.460 --> 07:14.928
UH, THANKS.

07:16.430 --> 07:18.421
WELL, OKAY, HONEY.

07:18.430 --> 07:19.795
IF IT'S WHAT YOU WANT.

07:19.800 --> 07:21.893
IT'S YOUR FUNERAL.

07:34.600 --> 07:36.591
LOOK, SHE GAVE ME
HER CARD.

07:36.600 --> 07:40.252
"SPIRITUAL CONSULTATION
AND PAST LIFE REGRESSION".

07:40.260 --> 07:41.989
OH, FOR GOD'S SAKE,
WHO DOES THIS ?

07:42.000 --> 07:45.322
WHO SPENDS $100 TO BE TOLD THEY
WERE ONCE ELEANOR OF AQUITAINE ?

07:45.330 --> 07:49.528
OR WHOEVER,
THE MARQUIS DE SADE.

07:49.530 --> 07:52.556
SO, WHAT DO YOU THINK
HAPPENS AFTER WE DIE ?

07:52.560 --> 07:54.653
HEAVEN ?
OR HELL.

07:54.660 --> 07:56.196
REALLY ?
WELL, YEAH.

07:56.200 --> 07:59.021
YEAH, BUT WITH LIKE
ANGELS AND DEVILS

07:59.030 --> 08:00.793
OR BRIMSTONE,
OR WHATEVER ?

08:00.800 --> 08:02.199
I DON'T KNOW WHAT IT LOOKS LIKE,
OR WHO ELSE IS THERE,

08:02.200 --> 08:03.690
BUT YES, I DO BELIEVE
THERE ARE CONSEQUENCES

08:03.700 --> 08:05.292
FOR THE WAY
WE LIVE OUR LIVES.

08:05.300 --> 08:06.790
HUH.

08:10.560 --> 08:12.494
YOU KNOW, SOMETIMES
I KIND OF FEEL LIKE...

08:12.500 --> 08:15.060
DAD'S AROUND.

08:17.430 --> 08:19.591
DO YOU, EVER ?

08:21.230 --> 08:22.754
NOPE.

08:25.830 --> 08:27.388
YOU KNOW,
WE HAVE

08:27.400 --> 08:29.254
THE INDEPENDENT
FUNERAL DIRECTORS
LUNCH TODAY, RIGHT ?

08:29.260 --> 08:31.091
MAN, WHY DO
I HAVE TO GO ?

08:31.100 --> 08:32.499
THAT'S YOUR THING.

08:32.500 --> 08:34.127
IT'S YOUR THING TOO NOW,
THESE ARE YOUR COLLEAGUES.

08:34.130 --> 08:35.358
IT'S IMPORTANT
TO KNOW WHO THEY ARE.

08:35.360 --> 08:36.452
I KNOW WHO THEY ARE.

08:36.460 --> 08:37.552
I MET THEM IN VEGAS,
THEY'RE FREAKS.

08:37.560 --> 08:40.256
THEY'RE NOT FREAKS.

08:40.260 --> 08:42.251
NOBODY LIKES
THE BRAZIL NUTS, DAVID.

08:42.260 --> 08:44.728
NOT THE LOCAL GUYS.

08:44.730 --> 08:46.527
OH YEAH, I'M SURE
THE L.A. MORTICIANS

08:46.530 --> 08:48.327
ARE A LOT MORE FUN
THAN THE GUYS FROM MONTANA.

08:48.330 --> 08:51.652
YOU'RE AN L.A. MORTICIAN NOW,
NATE, THIS IS YOUR COMMUNITY.

08:51.660 --> 08:54.026
YOU KNOW, IT'S POLITE
FOR THE FIRST PERSON DOWNSTAIRS

08:54.030 --> 08:55.429
TO MAKE THE COFFEE.

08:55.430 --> 08:57.193
EVEN IF THAT PERSON
HAS A PENIS.

08:57.200 --> 08:58.997
WELL, YOU KNOW, IT'S ALSO
POLITE FOR THE FIRST PERSON

08:59.000 --> 09:01.059
WHO USES THE BATHROOM TO SPEND
LESS THAN 45 MINUTES IN THERE,

09:01.060 --> 09:04.154
EVEN IF THAT PERSON
HAS A VULVA.

09:05.460 --> 09:07.291
OH, GOODNESS,
EVERYONE'S HERE.

09:07.300 --> 09:08.927
WITH ALL
THEIR GENITALIA.

09:08.930 --> 09:10.352
EXCUSE ME ?

09:10.360 --> 09:11.918
MOM, WOULD YOU
LIKE SOME TOAST ?

09:11.930 --> 09:14.296
NO, THANKS, I HAVE TO BE
IN THE VALLEY BY 10:30.

09:14.300 --> 09:15.949
WHAT'S IN THE VALLEY ?

09:15.960 --> 09:17.496
I'M GOING
TO A SEMINAR.

09:17.500 --> 09:18.558
WHAT SEMINAR ?

09:18.560 --> 09:20.050
OH, SOMETHING ROBBIE
INVITED ME TO,

09:20.060 --> 09:21.152
THE PLAN ?

09:21.160 --> 09:22.696
ISN'T THAT,
LIKE, A CULT ?

09:22.700 --> 09:24.327
NO, IT'S ONE OF THOSE
SELF-ACTUALIZATION THINGS

09:24.330 --> 09:26.798
FROM THE 705 WHERE
THEY YELL AT YOU FOR 12 HOURS

09:26.800 --> 09:28.199
AND DON'T LET YOU
GO TO THE BATHROOM.

09:28.200 --> 09:29.656
OH NO, REALLY ?

09:29.660 --> 09:31.457
SHOULD I BRING
SOME KIND OF JAR ?

09:31.460 --> 09:32.495
AJAR?

09:32.500 --> 09:34.252
I SUPPOSE THAT'S
NOT MUCH OF A SOLUTION.

09:34.260 --> 09:36.797
OH, AND YOU'RE ON
YOUR OWN FOR DINNER.

09:36.800 --> 09:39.325
I WON'T BE BACK
UNTIL AFI'ER MIDNIGHT.

09:40.860 --> 09:42.623
THE THOUGHT OF MOM
BEING SELF-ACTUALIZED

09:42.630 --> 09:44.450
IS KIND OF
MAKING ME NAUSEOUS.

09:44.460 --> 09:47.190
YOU SURE IT'S NOT THE THOUGHT
OF MOM PISSING INTO A JAR ?

09:50.760 --> 09:53.422
SO, TAHIRA, WHY CAN'T YOU
FORGIVE YOUR FATHER ?

09:53.430 --> 09:57.924
WHEN I WAS 16, HE HAD A DREAM
THAT I HAD GIVEN MYSELF TO A MAN

09:57.930 --> 10:01.559
WHO WAS NOT THE HUSBAND
I HAD BEEN PROMISED TO.

10:01.560 --> 10:04.825
FOR THAT,
HE SET ME ON FIRE.

10:04.830 --> 10:07.594
I WAS ABLE
TO SAVE MYSELF,

10:07.600 --> 10:12.424
BUT I HAD TO LEAVE THE COUNTRY
SO, HE WOULD NOT KILL ME.

10:14.260 --> 10:16.421
AND ALWAYS...

10:18.460 --> 10:20.655
I WILL HAVE THE SCARS
FROM THIS.

10:20.660 --> 10:21.991
THAT'S HORRIBLE.

10:22.000 --> 10:23.797
TRULY HORRIBLE.

10:23.800 --> 10:25.256
HOW COULD
HE DO THIS TO ME ?

10:25.260 --> 10:27.820
BUT AS LONG AS YOU HOLD ONTO
THAT ANGER TOWARD YOUR FATHER,

10:27.830 --> 10:30.094
YOU WILL BE ON FIRE.

10:30.100 --> 10:32.352
YOU MAY HAVE
LEFI' THE COUNTRY,

10:32.360 --> 10:35.693
BUT YOU'RE STILL
LIVING IN THE SAME HOUSE.

10:35.700 --> 10:37.349
AND IN THAT HOUSE

10:37.360 --> 10:39.794
THERE IS A ROOM
THAT IS STILL BURNING.

10:39.800 --> 10:41.199
WHO LIVES
IN THIS ROOM ?

10:41.200 --> 10:43.350
IDO?

10:43.360 --> 10:46.921
YOUR FATHER IS STILL
LIVING IN THIS ROOM.

10:46.930 --> 10:49.455
SO, YOU NEVER
INVITE ANYONE IN

10:49.460 --> 10:51.894
AND YOU GO
THROUGH LIFE ALONE.

10:51.900 --> 10:54.095
YOU MUST
OPEN THAT DOOR,

10:54.100 --> 10:55.499
PUT OUT THE FLAMES.

10:55.500 --> 10:57.718
YOU MUST INVITE YOUR FATHER
TO COME VISIT YOU.

10:57.730 --> 11:00.949
BUT HE WON'T
EVEN SPEAK TO ME.

11:00.960 --> 11:03.849
THAT IS
YOUR OLD BLUEPRINT !

11:03.860 --> 11:06.499
THAT IS WHAT
YOU WANT TO BELIEVE,

11:06.500 --> 11:08.422
BECAUSE YOU
ARE TOO AFRAID

11:08.430 --> 11:11.194
TO TEAR DOWN THE WALLS
AND REBUILD.

11:11.200 --> 11:12.599
OH, COME ON !

11:12.600 --> 11:14.056
STOP BLAMING
THE VICTIM !

11:14.060 --> 11:17.894
ALRIGHT, WHO HERE
THINKS I'M BEING UNFAIR ?

11:19.660 --> 11:21.628
BE HONEST.

11:28.330 --> 11:30.389
RUTH, DO YOU AGREE ?

11:30.400 --> 11:32.322
UNTIL TAHIRA
FORGIVES HER FATHER,

11:32.330 --> 11:36.391
SHE WILL NEVER FEEL SAFE
IN HER HOME ?

11:36.400 --> 11:38.493
WELL, MAYBE, BUT--

11:38.500 --> 11:39.626
SPEAK UP !

11:39.630 --> 11:41.325
WE ALL PAID TO HEAR YOU.

11:41.330 --> 11:43.798
WHY DON'T YOU STAND ?

11:47.360 --> 11:49.419
HER FATHER DID
SUCH A TERRIBLE THING.

11:49.430 --> 11:52.854
I DON'T SEE WHY SHE HAS
TO HAVE HIM AS A HOUSE GUEST.

11:52.860 --> 11:56.057
IF YOU DON'T AGREE WITH ME,
WHY DIDN'T RAISE YOUR HAND ?

11:56.060 --> 11:58.927
I WAS JUST TRYING
TO UNDERSTAND YOUR POINT.

11:58.930 --> 12:01.558
OR DO YOU THINK THAT YOUR
OPINION DOESN'T MATTER ?

12:01.560 --> 12:04.393
THAT PERHAPS YOU ARE
JUST A GUEST HERE ?

12:04.400 --> 12:07.426
ARE YOU A GUEST
IN YOUR OWN HOUSE, RUTH ?

12:07.430 --> 12:08.749
I DON'T THINK SO--

12:08.760 --> 12:09.692
YES.

12:09.700 --> 12:11.122
SHE TIPTOES
AROUND HERSELF

12:11.130 --> 12:13.428
LIKE SHE'S AFRAID
OF WAKING SOMEONE UP.

12:13.430 --> 12:16.024
THE ONLY PERSON SLEEPING
IN YOUR HOUSE IS YOU.

12:16.030 --> 12:17.497
WELL, I DO HAVE
THREE CHILDREN...

12:17.500 --> 12:19.149
SEE, SHE'S NOT
EVEN LISTENING.

12:19.160 --> 12:20.457
RUTH.

12:20.460 --> 12:21.825
YOU HAVE TO GET
OUT OF BED,

12:21.830 --> 12:25.698
OPEN THE WINDOWS AND LET
SOME LIGHT INTO YOUR HOUSE,

12:25.700 --> 12:28.954
SO, THAT YOU CAN
SEE THE WAY THINGS ARE.

12:28.960 --> 12:30.928
THEN AND ONLY THEN

12:30.930 --> 12:34.957
CAN YOU BEGIN
RENOVATING YOUR LIFE.

12:36.460 --> 12:37.654
SO, TAHIRA...

12:37.660 --> 12:40.299
ARE YOU READY
TO RENOVATE ?

12:40.300 --> 12:42.120
YES, I THINK SO.

12:42.130 --> 12:45.156
SO, WHEN YOU CALL YOUR FATHER,
WHAT WILL YOU SAY FIRST ?

12:45.160 --> 12:47.299
UH, HELLO ?

12:48.200 --> 12:50.395
SORRY,
MY BEAKER EXPLODED.

12:50.400 --> 12:51.924
THAT'S OKAY.

12:51.930 --> 12:53.522
CATCH YOUR BREATH.

12:54.900 --> 12:56.219
SO?

12:56.230 --> 12:58.198
HOW'S IT GOING ?

12:58.200 --> 13:01.795
UM, WELL, I HAVE
HYDROCHLORIC ACID
IN MY HAIR, BUT...

13:01.800 --> 13:03.893
OTHER THAN THAT,
I'M FINE.

13:03.900 --> 13:06.255
REALLY ?

13:06.260 --> 13:09.457
NO, BUT I'M INCREDIBLY BORED
WITH MYSELF RIGHT NOW.

13:11.260 --> 13:13.057
LET'S TALK ABOUT YOU.

13:13.060 --> 13:15.324
HOW'S YOUR GIRLFRIEND,
WHAT'S HER NAME ?

13:15.330 --> 13:16.695
JENNY.

13:16.700 --> 13:18.122
AND WE'RE FINE,
THAN KS.

13:18.130 --> 13:19.654
HOW'S IT GOING
WITH GABRIEL ?

13:19.660 --> 13:21.218
I HAVE NO IDEA.

13:21.230 --> 13:22.697
I HAVEN'T EVEN TALKED
TO HIM IN LIKE TWO WEEKS.

13:27.130 --> 13:28.256
IS THAT HER ?

13:28.260 --> 13:29.056
MM-HMM.

13:30.730 --> 13:31.628
WHAT DOES SHE DO ?

13:31.630 --> 13:33.427
SHE'S A JEWELRY DESIGNER.

13:33.430 --> 13:34.419
REALLY ?

13:34.430 --> 13:35.590
DOES SHE HAVE,
LIKE, A STORE ?

13:35.600 --> 13:37.818
NO, SHE HAS CLIENTS.

13:37.830 --> 13:39.297
AND SHE CATERS.

13:39.300 --> 13:43.350
BUT WE'RE NOT HERE
TO TALK ABOUT JENNY.

13:46.100 --> 13:47.692
LOOK, I THINK IT MIGHT HELP
TO TELL ME WHAT IT IS

13:47.700 --> 13:49.554
THAT YOU'RE GOING
THROUGH RIGHT NOW.

13:49.560 --> 13:51.926
WELL, IT'S NO
BIG FUCKING MYSTERY.

13:51.930 --> 13:54.125
I MEAN, IT SUCKS.

13:55.300 --> 13:58.599
IT SUCKS TO BE PRETTY MUCH,
YOU KNOW, IN LOVE WITH A GUY

13:58.600 --> 14:00.227
WHO'S TOO FUCKED UP
FOR LIFE, YOU KNOW ?

14:00.230 --> 14:01.993
WHAT HAPPENED ?

14:02.000 --> 14:04.195
NOTHING, REALLY, JUST...

14:04.200 --> 14:05.519
WHATEVER.

14:05.530 --> 14:07.828
YOU KNOW, IT'S NOT
EVEN HIS FAULT,

14:07.830 --> 14:09.229
IT FUCKING
PISSES ME OFF.

14:09.230 --> 14:10.822
THE WHOLE THING,
HIS WHOLE FAMILY THING

14:10.830 --> 14:12.559
IS SO FUCKING UNFAIR.

14:12.560 --> 14:15.723
I REALLY JUST THOUGHT HE JUST
NEEDED, LIKE, I DON'T KNOW...

14:15.730 --> 14:16.924
YOU ?

14:16.930 --> 14:17.851
NO.

14:17.860 --> 14:19.623
BUT SOMEONE, MAYBE.

14:19.630 --> 14:21.825
YOU KNOW, SOME PERSON
ON THE PLANET

14:21.830 --> 14:23.252
WHO GIVES A FUCK
ABOUT HIM.

14:23.260 --> 14:24.591
FOR ONCE IN HIS LIFE,

14:24.600 --> 14:26.227
YEAH, I DID THINK
MAYBE THAT WOULD MATI'ER.

14:26.230 --> 14:27.356
IT DOES MATTER.

14:27.360 --> 14:30.557
BUT NO ONE CAN EVER SOLVE
SOMEONE ELSE'S LIFE.

14:30.560 --> 14:33.597
SO, BASICALLY YOUR JOB
IS TOTALLY POINTLESS.

14:35.100 --> 14:38.354
NO ONE, BUT
A GUIDANCE COUNSELOR,
I MEAN.

14:42.860 --> 14:43.792
THERE THEY ARE.

14:43.800 --> 14:44.949
THAT'S THE
"COMMUNITY" ?

14:44.960 --> 14:46.325
I THOUGHT THIS WAS
SUPPOSED TO BE AN EVENT.

14:46.330 --> 14:47.729
OH, IT'S AN EVENT.

14:51.960 --> 14:53.518
DIDN'T I MEET ONE OF
THOSE GUYS IN VEGAS ?

14:53.530 --> 14:55.225
BOBO FROM
PEACEFUL HAVEN.

14:55.230 --> 14:57.221
RIGHT, HE SPITS.

14:57.230 --> 14:58.424
YES, HE DOES.

14:58.430 --> 14:59.522
HEY !

14:59.530 --> 15:00.895
STAN, JACK, BOBO,

15:00.900 --> 15:02.720
THIS IS MY BROTHER, NATE.

15:02.730 --> 15:04.322
NICE TO SEE YA, NATE.

15:04.330 --> 15:05.524
NICE TO MEET YOU, JACK.

15:05.530 --> 15:06.554
BOBO.

15:06.560 --> 15:08.096
GOOD SEEING YOU, BOBO.

15:08.100 --> 15:12.025
HEY, CONGRATULATIONS, WE HEARD
YOU JUST GOT YOUR LICENSE

15:12.030 --> 15:14.351
TO OPERATE
A MOVING FUNERAL.

15:14.360 --> 15:16.624
YEP, FINALLY WENT PRO.

15:16.630 --> 15:18.029
SIT, SIT, SIT !

15:18.030 --> 15:18.997
OH, NO, GO AHEAD.

