WELL, WE CERTAINLY DON'T
INTERRUPT OUR CLASSMATES.

28:32.430 --> 28:34.022
GO AHEAD.

28:34.030 --> 28:35.691
UM...

28:35.700 --> 28:38.999
WELL, IN YOUR DISCUSSION OF
BISEXUAL GENITAL RUBBING

28:39.000 --> 28:40.228
AMONG PYGMIE CHIMPS...

28:40.230 --> 28:41.822
YOU NOTE THE EXCHANGE
OF SEX FOR MEAT.

28:41.830 --> 28:44.754
AND WELL, I WAS WONDERING
HOW THIS MIGHT PERTAIN

28:44.760 --> 28:46.648
TO CONTEMPORARY
HUMAN BEHAVIOR.

28:46.660 --> 28:48.196
ANY TH EORIES ?

28:48.200 --> 28:49.394
IN CHAPTER...

28:53.930 --> 28:58.026
SO, WHERE DO YOU
THINK HE IS NOW ?

28:58.030 --> 29:02.148
ACCORDING TO HIS WIFE,
HE'S STILL HERE.

29:02.160 --> 29:05.493
WELL, THERE'S A BIG CHUNK OF
DEAD MEAT IN A CHEAP-O BOX

29:05.500 --> 29:07.297
THAT'S STILL HERE.

29:07.300 --> 29:09.894
BUT DO YOU REALLY
BELIEVE THAT'S HIM ?

29:09.900 --> 29:11.959
THE ESSENCE OF
WHO HE WAS ?

29:11.960 --> 29:14.326
THE PART OF HIM
THAT HOPED AND DREAMED

29:14.330 --> 29:16.150
AND ALL THAT
OTHER CRAP ?

29:16.160 --> 29:19.391
YOU TELL ME, YOU'RE THE ONE
WHO HAS ALL THE ANSWERS NOW.

29:19.400 --> 29:20.856
I NEVER SAID THAT.

29:20.860 --> 29:22.623
YOU'D THINK
GETTING HAMMERED BY A BUS

29:22.630 --> 29:25.952
WOULD MAKE YOU
A LITTLE LESS OF A DICK.

29:25.960 --> 29:30.158
SURE, IT'S POSSIBLE THAT
WE GO ON AFTER WE DIE...

29:31.100 --> 29:33.853
BUT IT'S ALSO POSSIBLE
THAT ONCE THE LIGHT GOES OUT,

29:33.860 --> 29:35.589
IT STAYS OUT.

29:35.600 --> 29:38.956
YOU'LL NEVER KNOW, BUDDY-BOY,
'TIL IT'S YOUR TURN.

29:38.960 --> 29:41.520
SEE, THAT'S WHAT
YOU WERE HANGING ON TO.

29:41.530 --> 29:43.418
EXCUSE ME ?

29:43.430 --> 29:45.853
MICHAEL.

29:45.860 --> 29:46.997
IS HE HERE ?

29:47.000 --> 29:48.797
HE'S BEEN WITH ME
THE WHOLE TIME.

29:48.800 --> 29:51.792
YOU THINK
HE'LL STAY WITH YOU ?

29:51.800 --> 29:53.654
NOT LIKE THIS.

29:53.660 --> 29:57.118
HE'S JUST HELPING ME
GET USED TO IT.

29:59.200 --> 30:00.895
DO YOU-- LOOK,
I HOPE YOU DON'T MIND,

30:00.900 --> 30:04.449
BUT DO YOU GET A SENSE OF
MY FATHER, AT ALL, AROUND HERE ?

30:19.060 --> 30:21.119
NO, I'M SORRY.

30:21.130 --> 30:23.018
BUT THAT DOESN'T
MEAN HE'S NOT HERE.

30:23.030 --> 30:24.395
THIS ROOM IS PACKED.

30:24.400 --> 30:26.721
I CAN'T GET
TO EVERYONE.

30:28.330 --> 30:29.729
I THINK EVERYTHING
IS READY.

30:29.730 --> 30:34.121
I DO SEE A CHILD
COMING INTO YOUR LIFE.

30:34.130 --> 30:35.597
NO.

30:35.600 --> 30:37.022
IT MIGHT BE YOU.

30:37.030 --> 30:39.123
OH, I SERIOUSLY
DOUBT THAT.

30:39.130 --> 30:41.792
WELL, I'M NOT SURE
WHICH ONE OF YOU I'M READING.

30:41.800 --> 30:45.918
BUT I'M QUITE SURE THERE'S GONNA
BE A CHILD HERE VERY SOON.

30:45.930 --> 30:49.457
HEY, I'M HEADING
OUT NOW, OKAY ?

30:49.460 --> 30:52.452
THIS IS FEDERICO DIAZ,
OUR EMBALMER.

30:52.460 --> 30:54.291
AND HIS BABY, AUGUSTO.

30:54.300 --> 30:55.927
THIS IS MRS. PIPER.

30:55.930 --> 30:57.852
OH, OH, HI.

30:57.860 --> 30:59.657
I'M SORRY
FOR YOUR LOSS.

30:59.660 --> 31:00.592
THANK YOU.

31:00.600 --> 31:02.522
YOU MADE HIS BODY
LOOK VERY NICE.

31:02.530 --> 31:03.997
THANK YOU.

31:04.000 --> 31:06.218
ACTUALLY, HIS BODY
GAVE ME A LOT TO WORK WITH.

31:06.230 --> 31:08.892
HARDLY ANY DECAY
FOR A CANCER DEATH.

31:08.900 --> 31:10.094
IT'S USUALLY--

31:10.100 --> 31:11.954
OKAY, RICO,
SEE YOU TOMORROW.

31:11.960 --> 31:13.496
YEAH, OKAY,
NICE TO MEET YOU, MA'AM.

31:13.500 --> 31:16.151
( baby crying )

31:16.160 --> 31:17.821
LET'S GO.

31:18.960 --> 31:20.791
HERE WE GO.

31:26.000 --> 31:28.696
EILEEN ASKED THAT I CLOSE
WITH A READING

31:28.700 --> 31:31.521
FROM MICHAEL'S FAVORITE POET,
WALT WHITMAN.

31:34.130 --> 31:36.724
"WHAT DO YOU THINK HAS BECOME
OF THE YOUNG AND OLD MEN ?

31:36.730 --> 31:38.357
"AND WHAT DO YOU THINK

31:38.360 --> 31:40.453
"HAS BECOME OF
THE WOMEN AND CHILDREN ?

31:40.460 --> 31:43.588
"THEY ARE ALIVE
AND WELL SOMEWHERE,

31:43.600 --> 31:47.252
"THE SMALLEST SPROUT SHOWS
THERE IS REALLY NO DEATH,

31:47.260 --> 31:50.320
"AND IF EVER THERE WAS
IT LED FORWARD LIFE,

31:50.330 --> 31:52.457
"AND DOES NOT WAIT
AT THE END TO ARREST IT,

31:52.460 --> 31:55.224
"AND CEASED THE MOMENT
LIFE APPEARED.

31:55.230 --> 31:57.892
"ALL GOES ONWARD
AND OUTWARD,

31:57.900 --> 31:59.424
"NOTHING COLLAPSES,

31:59.430 --> 32:01.250
"AND TO DIE
IS DIFFERENT

32:01.260 --> 32:03.649
"FROM WHAT
ANYONE SUPPOSED,

32:03.660 --> 32:06.026
AND LUCKIER."

32:07.660 --> 32:09.651
LET US PRAY.

32:11.430 --> 32:15.548
OH, LORD, BLESS THE DEPARTED
SOUL OF OUR BROTHER, FRIEND...

32:15.560 --> 32:19.599
I'M JUST HANGING AROUND
TO HELP YOU GET USED IT.

32:19.600 --> 32:22.421
I AM USED TO IT, DAD,
IT'S BEEN SIX MONTHS.

32:22.430 --> 32:23.897
SEVEN.

32:23.900 --> 32:26.357
NOT THAT
YOU'RE COUNTING.

32:31.130 --> 32:32.927
AMEN.

32:32.930 --> 32:35.023
( together )
AMEN.

32:43.900 --> 32:45.299
HEY.

32:45.300 --> 32:47.393
HEY, ARE YOU DONE ?

32:47.400 --> 32:48.594
PRETTY MUCH,
WHAT'S UP ?

32:48.600 --> 32:51.398
WELL, I WANTED
TO ASK YOU SOMETHING.

32:51.400 --> 32:52.526
OKAY.

32:52.530 --> 32:54.350
GET THIS,
BOBO SOLD TO KROEHNER.

32:54.360 --> 32:56.999
BOBO SOLD,
MY BOBO ?

32:57.000 --> 32:58.297
YOUR BOBO.

32:58.300 --> 33:01.952
I CAN'T BELIEVE THIS,
HE WAS SO COMMITTED.

33:02.430 --> 33:05.957
YOU THINK HE'S GOT
A PLASTIC SCREW
IN HIS ANUS ABOUT NOW ?

33:05.960 --> 33:06.995
I HOPE SO.

33:07.000 --> 33:09.025
SONOFABITCH,
I'M GONNA GO CALL HIM.

33:12.330 --> 33:14.195
WHAT'S THE MATTER
WITH YOU ?

33:14.200 --> 33:15.622
NOTHING.

33:20.130 --> 33:21.358
WHERE'S KARLA ?

33:21.360 --> 33:23.055
SHE'S JUST
WORKING LATE.

33:23.060 --> 33:24.391
WHY YOU FRONTIN' ?

33:24.400 --> 33:26.857
GO TO YOUR ROOM NOW,
TAYLOR.

33:26.860 --> 33:29.294
MAMA HASN'T
BEEN HOME SINCE TUESDAY.

33:29.300 --> 33:30.790
WHAT ?

33:30.800 --> 33:32.097
NOW.

33:32.100 --> 33:33.556
BUT MY STOMACH HURTS.

33:33.560 --> 33:35.323
I'LL GET YOU
SOME PEPTO BISMOL.

33:35.330 --> 33:37.491
I DON'T WANT NONE OF
THAT NASTY SHIT.

33:37.500 --> 33:39.252
THEN GO ON.

33:39.260 --> 33:42.525
SHIT, BITCH,
I GOTTA GET MY GOODS !

33:42.530 --> 33:45.397
HEY, DON'T TALK
TO YOUR GRANDMOTHER LIKE THAT.

33:45.400 --> 33:49.097
"DON'T TALK TO
YOUR GRANDMOTHER LIKE THAT."

33:49.100 --> 33:50.055
( door slamming )

33:50.060 --> 33:51.254
SHE'S SICK ?

33:51.260 --> 33:52.591
SHE SAYS
THAT EVERY NIGHT.

33:52.600 --> 33:54.192
SHE JUST
WANTS THE ATTENTION.

33:54.200 --> 33:55.599
CAN YOU BLAME HER ?

33:55.600 --> 33:57.659
HER MOTHER'S OFF DOING
GOD KNOWS WHATEVER.

33:57.660 --> 33:59.093
KARLA'S FINE.

33:59.100 --> 34:00.727
SHE JUST HAD
TO GO OUT OF TOWN.

34:00.730 --> 34:01.992
OH, YOU TALKED TO HER ?

34:02.000 --> 34:03.558
I WASN'T IN
WHEN SHE CALLED.

34:03.560 --> 34:04.822
BUT SHE LEFT
SEVERAL MESSAGES.

34:04.830 --> 34:06.855
BESIDES, I'M HERE
WITH TAYLOR.

34:06.860 --> 34:08.828
DON'T BLOW THIS OUT OF
PROPORTION LIKE YOU ALWAYS DO.

34:08.830 --> 34:11.219
( beeping )
Hey, Mama.

34:11.230 --> 34:13.095
I'm not coming
home tonight.

34:13.100 --> 34:14.692
Derrick needs
his papers...

34:14.700 --> 34:16.952
CAN'T SHE SEND HIM
HIS PAPERS ?

34:16.960 --> 34:18.621
WELL, YOU REMEMBER
HOW DERRICK WAS,

34:18.630 --> 34:21.155
ALWAYS GETTING HER
TO DO THIS AND THAT FOR HIM.

34:21.160 --> 34:24.197
YEAH, LIKE RAISE HIS KID
WITHOUT A DIME FROM HIM.

34:24.200 --> 34:26.088
Sorry, I dropped
the phone.

34:26.100 --> 34:27.328
Shut up.

34:27.330 --> 34:28.558
Anyway,

34:28.560 --> 34:29.959
I'll call you
as soon as I can.

34:29.960 --> 34:31.222
Okay ?

34:31.230 --> 34:33.596
OKAY, WE CAN GET
THE PHONE COMPANY RECORDS,

34:33.600 --> 34:36.524
BUT I'LL HAVE TO FILE
A MISSING PERSONS REPORT FIRST.

34:36.530 --> 34:39.556
KEITH, WHY MUST YOU ALWAYS
THINK THE WORST OF HER ?!

34:39.560 --> 34:41.892
LET'S JUST WAIT
'TIL SHE GETS HOME.

34:41.900 --> 34:43.458
WE DON'T EVEN KNOW--

34:43.460 --> 34:44.757
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO,

34:44.760 --> 34:46.523
MOVE UP HERE AND TAKE CARE
OF HER THE REST OF YOUR LIFE ?

34:46.530 --> 34:48.725
SHE HAS A CHILD, JESUS,
SHE NEEDS HELP !

34:48.730 --> 34:50.755
AND YOU COVERING UP FOR HER
IS NOT WHAT I MEAN !

34:50.760 --> 34:52.352
WHO DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE TALKING TO ?

34:52.360 --> 34:54.248
I AM YOUR MOTHER

34:54.260 --> 34:56.455
AND YOU WILL
RESPECT THAT

34:56.460 --> 34:58.724
OR I WILL SMACK THE BLACK
RIGHT OFF OF YOU !

35:12.300 --> 35:14.120
HI, THERE.

35:15.260 --> 35:17.194
HI.

35:18.130 --> 35:19.927
HARD DAY ?

35:21.960 --> 35:23.518
HOW CAN YOU TELL ?

35:23.530 --> 35:26.624
I'M GOOD AT PEOPLE.

35:30.630 --> 35:31.995
ARE YOU ?

35:32.000 --> 35:34.696
GOT TO BE,
TAX LAW.

35:36.600 --> 35:37.851
I'M SCOTT.

35:37.860 --> 35:39.293
SCOTT AXELROD.

35:39.300 --> 35:40.858
CAN DACE BOUVARD.

35:40.860 --> 35:42.725
NICE TO MEET YOU,
CANDACE.

35:42.730 --> 35:45.119
ARE YOU AN ACTRESS ?

35:47.330 --> 35:49.491
OH, NO.

35:49.500 --> 35:53.891
I TEACH SIGN LANGUAGE
TO THE NEWLY DEAF.

35:54.630 --> 35:56.052
REALLY ?

36:01.530 --> 36:03.157
HOW NOBLE.

36:03.160 --> 36:05.856
OH, NO,
IT'S VERY LUCRATIVE.

36:05.860 --> 36:09.557
AND I REALLY ENJOY
COMMUNICATING WITH MY BODY.

36:12.800 --> 36:14.529
I GET THAT.

36:20.000 --> 36:21.854
OH, YOU KNOW WHAT,
MY FRIEND IS HERE.

36:21.860 --> 36:24.556
BUT IT'S BEEN REALLY GREAT
GETTING TO KNOW YOU, SCOTT.

36:24.560 --> 36:27.120
I WOULD LOVE TO TAKE YOU
TO DINNER SOMETIME.

36:27.130 --> 36:28.552
CAN I GIVE YOU
MY CARD ?

36:28.560 --> 36:30.198
YOU SURE CAN.

36:36.160 --> 36:37.889
HOW WAS SCHOOL ?

36:37.900 --> 36:40.391
IT WAS
A DISASTER.

36:41.930 --> 36:43.693
ALRIG HT,

36:43.700 --> 36:45.622
YOU HAVE 20 MINUTES TO DO
WHAT'S MOST IMPORTANT

36:45.630 --> 36:47.257
IN YOUR LIFE NOW.

36:47.260 --> 36:49.490
WHAT DID YOU WRITE TO YOURSELF
IN YOUR PRIVATE LETTER ?

36:49.500 --> 36:51.798
WHERE ARE YOU LOCKED
OUT OF YOUR OWN LIFE ?

36:51.800 --> 36:54.155
IF YOU LEARNED TODAY THAT YOUR
RELATIONSHIP WITH YOUR MOTHER

36:54.160 --> 36:56.390
HAS BEEN BLOCKING THE DOOR
TO YOUR HAPPINESS,

36:56.400 --> 36:58.459
THEN MAKE THAT REPAIR.

36:58.460 --> 37:00.098
RIGHT NOW !

37:00.100 --> 37:03.058
WAITING ONLY GIVES YOU
MORE CHANCES TO MAKE EXCUSES.

37:04.330 --> 37:05.558
THERE ARE PHONES
IN THE HALL.

37:05.560 --> 37:07.858
SEE YOU IN
19 MINUTES.

37:08.660 --> 37:10.594
WHERE CAN I FIND
A SNICKER'S BAR ?

37:10.600 --> 37:13.296
CAN'T YOU THINK OF
MORE PRODUCT IVE WAYS

37:13.300 --> 37:15.120
TO USE THIS TIME ?

37:15.130 --> 37:16.893
LIKE WHAT,
TAKING UP SMOKING ?

37:16.900 --> 37:19.152
WHY NOT TRY REBUILDING
WITH SOMEONE RIGHT NOW ?

37:19.160 --> 37:21.424
RUTH...

37:21.430 --> 37:24.297
I READ YOUR PRIVATE
LETTER TO YOURSELF.

37:24.300 --> 37:27.394
AND IF YOU REALLY WANT
CLOSENESS IN YOUR LIFE,

37:27.400 --> 37:29.960
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO
START MAJOR RENOVATIONS.

37:29.960 --> 37:31.450
IN FACT, I WOULD GUT.

37:31.460 --> 37:32.825
YOU READ
MY PRIVATE LETTER ?

37:32.830 --> 37:34.525
WHY DON'T YOU
TRY CALLING YOUR KIDS ?

37:34.530 --> 37:36.794
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHERE MY KIDS ARE.

37:36.800 --> 37:38.791
AND THE LAST THING
ANY OF THEM WANTS IS

37:38.800 --> 37:40.153
FOR ME TO CALL THEM
ON A FRIDAY NIGHT

37:40.160 --> 37:42.025
SO, I CAN
PUT IN NEW FLOORING.

37:45.030 --> 37:46.258
OH, FUCK !

37:46.260 --> 37:49.297
I LOVE YOU TOO,
YOU SADISTIC OLD FUCK.

37:50.730 --> 37:52.425
START WITH CLAIRE.

37:52.430 --> 37:54.295
ONLY YOU...

37:54.300 --> 37:57.952
CAN BE THE ARCHITECT
OF YOUR LIFE.

38:15.500 --> 38:16.728
CLAIRE ?

38:16.730 --> 38:19.028
THIS IS YOUR MOTHER.

38:20.230 --> 38:23.757
YES, WELL, I JUST WANTED
TO TELL YOU THAT...

38:25.100 --> 38:27.955
I FEEL LIKE EVEN THOUGH I'VE
BEEN TRYING TO BE CLOSER TO YOU,

38:27.960 --> 38:30.895
IT HASN'T REALLY
BEEN WORKING.

38:32.660 --> 38:34.651
I WISH YOU FELT YOU COULD
CONFIDE IN ME.

38:34.660 --> 38:38.721
AND MAYBE YOU DON'T BECAUSE YOU
FEEL MY OPINION IS WORTHLESS.

38:40.260 --> 38:42.558
BECAUSE I DON'T
REALLY LIVE IN MY HOUSE,

38:42.560 --> 38:45.791
AND SO, I SUPPOSE

38:45.800 --> 38:48.496
THAT'S THE INFRASTRUCTURE
I BUILT.

38:48.500 --> 38:50.855
SO, I'M SORRY.

38:50.860 --> 38:52.953
AND ?

38:52.960 --> 38:56.054
AND, I LOVE YOU.

38:56.460 --> 38:59.554
THAT'S SO GOOD,
I GOTTA PEE LIKE A RACEHORSE.

39:01.430 --> 39:02.795
( male recording )
You have exceeded
the time limit !

39:02.800 --> 39:04.995
If you know the name of
the movie you'd like to see,

39:05.000 --> 39:06.991
press one now !

39:07.300 --> 39:12.522
YOU WERE RIGHT WHEN YOU SAID
ALL THAT GLITTERS ISN'T GOLD

39:14.700 --> 39:20.457
YOU WERE RIGHT WHEN YOU SAID
ALL WE ARE IS DUST IN THE WIND

39:20.460 --> 39:22.553
( phone )

39:25.160 --> 39:26.525
HELLO ?

39:26.530 --> 39:28.020
( Gabe )
Claire ?

39:28.030 --> 39:29.759
WHERE THE FUCK
HAVE YOU BEEN ?

39:29.760 --> 39:32.024
I fucked up.

39:32.030 --> 39:33.349
GABE, WHAT IS GOING ON ?

39:33.360 --> 39:37.729
Everything is all
fucked up, Claire.

39:37.730 --> 39:39.095
LOOK, IT'S GONNA BE OKAY,

39:39.100 --> 39:40.897
YOU JUST HAVE
TO CALM DOWN RIGHT NOW.

39:40.900 --> 39:42.424
I need...

39:42.430 --> 39:45.854
I need you to come
and get me, please !

39:47.230 --> 39:48.492
Please !

39:48.500 --> 39:51.719
YOU KNOW, THE COPS ARE, LIKE,
SERIOUSLY LOOKING FOR YOU.

39:51.730 --> 39:53.857
I know that, okay ?

39:53.860 --> 39:55.828
Why do you think I need you
to come out here and get me ?

39:55.830 --> 39:57.627
WHERE ARE YOU ?

39:57.630 --> 40:01.259
I'm up past
Woodland Hills.

40:01.900 --> 40:04.050
ACADEMIA IS
ONE HUGE CIRCLE JERK.

40:04.060 --> 40:06.893
ALL THESE SEQUESTERED PEOPLE
DESPERATELY DEFENDING

40:06.900 --> 40:10.199
THE ONE GOOD IDEA THEY HAVE
EVER HAD IN THEIR LIVES.

40:10.200 --> 40:11.895
SO, WHAT, THAT'S IT
FOR GOING BACK TO SCHOOL ?

40:11.900 --> 40:13.720
YEP.

40:13.730 --> 40:15.357
NEXT ?

40:21.760 --> 40:22.829
HOW WAS YOUR DAY ?

40:22.830 --> 40:24.149
IT WAS WEIRD.

40:24.160 --> 40:26.355
BURIED THAT PSYCHIC WOMAN'S
HUSBAND AND SHE WAS STILL, LIKE,

40:26.360 --> 40:27.827
TALKING TO THE GUY.

40:27.830 --> 40:29.024
OH, THAT'S SAD.

40:29.030 --> 40:30.258
NOT FOR HER, I MEAN.

40:30.260 --> 40:33.991
SHE REALLY BELIEVED
HE WAS THERE, YOU KNOW ?

40:34.000 --> 40:36.355
WELL, SHE HAS
TO SAY THAT, RIGHT ?

40:36.360 --> 40:38.658
IF SHE CLAIMS
SHE'S A PSYCHIC.

40:38.660 --> 40:40.252
YOU DON'T THINK THAT
THAT'S POSSIBLE ?

40:40.260 --> 40:42.751
WHAT ABOUT YOU SAYING THAT
THINGS HAPPEN THAT LEAVE MARKS

40:42.760 --> 40:45.797
IN PEOPLE,
IN PLACES,
IN TIME ?

40:45.800 --> 40:47.290
THAT'S PHYSICS,

40:47.300 --> 40:49.757
ENERGY AFFECTING MATTER.

40:49.760 --> 40:52.649
TALKING TO DEAD PEOPLE
IS DELUSIONAL.

40:52.660 --> 40:54.298
SO, YOU DEFINITELY
DON'T BELIEVE

40:54.300 --> 40:55.949
IN ANY KIND OF
LIFE-AFTER-DEATH THING ?

40:55.960 --> 40:59.589
I THINK PEOPLE LIVE ON
THROUGH THE PEOPLE THEY LOVE

40:59.600 --> 41:03.092
AND THE THINGS
THEY DO WITH THEIR LIVES.

41:03.100 --> 41:07.093
IF THEY MANAGE TO DO THINGS
WITH THEIR LIVES.

41:07.100 --> 41:10.592
BUT THAT'S IT, THAT'S IT,
THAT'S ALL THERE IS.

41:10.600 --> 41:12.818
THERE'S NOTHING MORE,
THERE'S NOTHING, LIKE, BIGGER ?

41:12.830 --> 41:14.195
JUST ENERGY.

41:14.200 --> 41:15.622
BUT THERE'S NO PLAN.

41:15.630 --> 41:18.451
NO, THERE'S
DEFINITELY NO PLAN.

41:21.100 --> 41:23.751
JUST SURVIVAL.

41:26.130 --> 41:28.155
SHOULD I HAVE
ORDERED THE SALMON ?

41:28.160 --> 41:30.856
UH, I DON'T KNOW.

41:33.330 --> 41:34.524
HOW CAN YOU
LIVE LIKE THAT ?

41:34.530 --> 41:37.124
WHAT IF YOU FOUND OUT
YOU WERE GONNA DIE TOMORROW ?

41:37.130 --> 41:38.791
I'VE BEEN PREPARED
TO DIE TOMORROW

41:38.800 --> 41:40.324
SINCE I WAS
SIX YEARS OLD.

41:40.330 --> 41:42.594
REALLY ?

41:42.600 --> 41:43.919
YEAH.

41:43.930 --> 41:46.421
PRETTY MUCH,
WE NEVER GOT BUTTER.

41:46.430 --> 41:48.125
WELL, WHY SINCE
YOU WERE SIX ?

41:48.130 --> 41:51.622
'CAUSE I READ A REPORT
ON THE EFFECT NUCLEAR WAR

41:51.630 --> 41:52.995
WOULD HAVE
ON THE WORLD.

41:53.000 --> 41:54.524
AND IT WAS PRETTY CLEAR TO ME,
AT THAT POINT,

41:54.530 --> 41:56.225
THAT THIS WAS DEFINITELY
GONNA HAPPEN.

41:56.230 --> 41:58.494
WHEN YOU WERE SIX ?

41:58.500 --> 42:02.527
AND I WAKE UP EVERY DAY
PRETTY MUCH SURPRISED THAT...

42:02.530 --> 42:06.091
EVERYTHING'S
STILL HERE.

42:06.100 --> 42:08.694
WELL, I DON'T UNDERSTAND
HOW YOU CAN LIVE LIKE THAT.

42:08.700 --> 42:12.693
WELL, I THOUGHT
WE ALL DID.

42:27.400 --> 42:28.822
WHO IS THAT ?

42:28.830 --> 42:30.320
I WENT TO HIGH SCHOOL
WITH HIM.

42:30.330 --> 42:33.356
HE'S CLEARLY
HAD A NOSE JOB.

42:36.930 --> 42:38.397
CLOSE YOUR EYES.

42:38.400 --> 42:40.220
GO ON.

42:40.230 --> 42:43.449
AND IMAGINE THAT
EVERYONE IN THIS ROOM

42:43.460 --> 42:45.519
THINKS YOU ARE
AN IDIOT.

42:45.530 --> 42:48.328
A TOTAL FOOL,
A COMPLETE MORON,
ABSOLUTE ASS.

42:50.160 --> 42:52.549
FEEL FAMILIAR ?

42:52.560 --> 42:54.721
IT'S HOW YOU FEEL
IN THE WORLD, ISN'T IT ?

42:54.730 --> 42:57.392
I WANT YOU TO
FEEL IT DEEPLY NOW.

42:57.400 --> 42:58.594
REALLY FEEL IT.

42:58.600 --> 43:00.522
EVERYONE IN THIS ROOM
THINKS YOU'RE AN IDIOT.

43:08.560 --> 43:10.152
CLOSE YOUR EYES, RUTH.

43:10.160 --> 43:12.492
FEEL YOU'RE AN IDIOT.

43:16.400 --> 43:18.152
NOW, TELL ME

43:18.160 --> 43:20.424
WHEN YOU GET THE JOKE.

43:23.600 --> 43:25.818
( laughing )

43:31.800 --> 43:33.153
DO YOU GET
THE JOKE, RUTH ?

43:33.160 --> 43:34.297
NO!

43:34.300 --> 43:35.699
I'M AN IDIOT !

43:35.700 --> 43:39.022
WHO WANTS TO EXPLAIN
THE JOKE TO RUTH ?

43:43.060 --> 43:45.597
SO, WE ALL FEEL
THE SAME WAY, RIGHT ?

43:45.600 --> 43:48.626
SO, WHO'S REALLY
THE ASSHOLE ?

43:48.630 --> 43:50.359
WE ALL ARE ?

43:50.360 --> 43:51.759
RUTH.

43:51.760 --> 43:53.091
STAND UP.

43:55.530 --> 43:58.454
TELL ME WHAT YOU WROTE IN YOUR
PRIVATE LETTER TO YOURSELF.

43:58.460 --> 44:00.894
IT WAS
A PRIVATE LETTER !

44:00.900 --> 44:02.299
TO MYSELF !

44:02.300 --> 44:05.019
TELL ME WHERE
YOUR HOUSE NEEDS REPAIRS !

44:05.030 --> 44:07.157
YEAH, AND DON'T BULLSHIT
THE LADY, CUPCAKE.

44:07.160 --> 44:10.618
I HAVE A VERY
NICE HOUSE !

44:10.630 --> 44:13.497
I HAVE NICE CHILDREN
AND A NICE JOB.

44:13.500 --> 44:16.060
AND A NICE
GENTLEMAN FRIEND.

44:16.060 --> 44:18.255
CAN'T ANYONE
JUST BE HAPPY ?

44:18.260 --> 44:20.592
I'M HAPPY.

44:20.600 --> 44:22.727
WHO'S BUYING
RUTH'S HOUSE ?

44:24.700 --> 44:27.260
WE DON'T BELIEVE YOUR HOUSE
IS STRUCTURALLY SOUND, RUTH.

44:27.260 --> 44:28.488
WHO KNOWS BETTER ?

44:28.500 --> 44:30.525
ME OR A ROOM
FULL OF COMPLAINERS ?

44:30.530 --> 44:33.124
WHAT DO YOU REALLY WANT
TO COMPLAIN ABOUT REALLY ?

44:33.130 --> 44:34.597
THE FACT THAT THE BLOOD
STOPPED CIRCULATING

44:34.600 --> 44:36.397
IN MY REAR END
FOUR HOURS AGO !

44:36.400 --> 44:38.721
OKAY, WHAT ELSE ?

44:38.730 --> 44:40.698
YOU WANT ME
TO COMPLAIN ?

44:40.700 --> 44:43.749
ALRIGHT THEN,
FUCK THIS !

44:43.760 --> 44:45.227
FUCK YOU.

44:45.230 --> 44:47.095
FUCK ALL OF YOU WITH
YOUR SNIVELING SELF-PITY.

44:47.100 --> 44:50.126
AND FUCK ALL
YOUR LOUSY PARENTS.

44:50.130 --> 44:52.451
FUCK MY LOUSY PARENTS,
WHILE WE'RE AT IT.

44:52.460 --> 44:56.294
FUCK MY SELFISH BOHEMIAN SISTER
AND HER FUCKING BLISS !

44:56.300 --> 44:58.029
FUCK MY LEGLESS
GRANDMOTHER !

44:58.030 --> 44:59.452
FUCK MY DEAD HUSBAND.

44:59.460 --> 45:02.190
AND MY LOUSY CHILDREN WITH
THEIR NASTY LITTLE SECRETS.

45:02.200 --> 45:05.852
AND FUCK YOU ROBBIE
FOR DRAGGING ME
TO THIS TERRIBLE PLACE

45:05.860 --> 45:07.851
AND NOT LETTING ME
HAVE A SNICKERS BAR !

45:07.860 --> 45:09.691
I'M GOING TO GET
SOMETHING TO EAT !

45:09.700 --> 45:12.999
CONGRATULATIONS, RUTH.

45:13.000 --> 45:16.049
YOU HAVE JUST LEVELED
YOUR FLEABAG HOVEL !

45:16.060 --> 45:20.190
NOW YOU CAN BUILD
THE HOUSE OF YOUR DREAMS
FROM THE GROUND UP !

45:20.200 --> 45:21.849
YES, YES !

45:21.860 --> 45:24.294
OH, EXCELLENT.

45:24.300 --> 45:27.019
CONGRATULATIONS.

45:53.960 --> 45:55.097
OH, JESUS.

45:56.200 --> 45:57.895
OKAY, LET'S HOP.

45:59.460 --> 46:00.996
UH, HI ?

46:01.000 --> 46:03.093
WE SHOULD,
WE SHOULD JUST GET GOING.

46:04.460 --> 46:07.497
OKAY, BUT YOU COULD TELL ME
WHERE THE FUCK YOU'VE BEEN FOR--

46:07.500 --> 46:09.752
LIKE YOU CARE.

46:10.760 --> 46:12.193
WHAT ?

46:12.200 --> 46:15.624
( laughing )
I JUST DRAGGED MY ASS
WAY THE FUCK OUT TO NOWHERE.

46:15.630 --> 46:18.929
CAN WE JUST TALK ABOUT THIS
WHILE WE'RE DRIVING ?

46:18.930 --> 46:20.693
OKAY ?

46:20.700 --> 46:23.157
JESUS.

46:23.160 --> 46:24.991
IT'S HOT AS HELL
IN THIS CAR.

46:41.260 --> 46:43.023
CAN YOU TELL ME
WHERE WE'RE GOING ?

46:43.030 --> 46:46.750
LET'S JUST HEAD OUT
TO ANGELA'S CREST OR SOMETHING.

46:46.760 --> 46:47.988
ANGELA'S CREST ?

46:48.000 --> 46:49.649
THAT'S LIKE WHERE SERIAL KILLERS
GO TO DUMP THE BODIES.

46:49.660 --> 46:51.753
YOU THINK YOU CAN THINK UP
SOMEPLACE A LITTLE CREEPIER ?

46:51.760 --> 46:52.954
I DON'T CARE
WHERE WE GO,

46:52.960 --> 46:54.689
I JUST WANT
TO GO SOMEWHERE

46:54.700 --> 46:56.429
WHERE WE CAN BE ALONE
FOR A MINUTE, AND WE CAN,

46:56.430 --> 46:58.955
JUST TALK, YOU KNOW,
AND JUST WHATEVER.

47:00.960 --> 47:03.121
ARE YOU FUCKED UP
RIGHT NOW ?

47:03.130 --> 47:04.620
WHAT THE FUCK
DO YOU EXPECT, CLAIRE ?

47:04.630 --> 47:07.394
OKAY, I'M FREAKED OUT,
YOU KNOW.

47:07.400 --> 47:09.197
EVERYTHING IS REALLY
FUCKED UP FOR ME RIGHT NOW.

47:09.200 --> 47:10.599
YEAH, OKAY, SO WHAT
ARE YOU GONNA DO ?

47:10.600 --> 47:12.420
I DON'T KNOW, THAT'S WHAT
I'M TRYING TO FIGURE OUT.

47:12.430 --> 47:13.658
WHAT IS THERE
TO FIGURE OUT ?

47:17.600 --> 47:20.296
LOOK, THEY KNOW
YOU GAVE ANDY THE FRY,

47:20.300 --> 47:22.154
OR WHATEVER THE FUCK
IT'S CALLED.

47:22.160 --> 47:24.196
THEY KNOW YOU
ROBBED THAT STORE, GABE.

47:25.530 --> 47:27.851
YOU HAVE
TO TURN YOURSELF IN.

47:27.860 --> 47:29.828
YEAH, OH, YEAH.

47:29.830 --> 47:32.492
THAT IS A GENIUS
FUCKING PLAN.

47:32.500 --> 47:33.626
HEY !

47:33.630 --> 47:34.995
HEY, BABY.

47:35.000 --> 47:36.820
YOU LIKE
TO DRINK BLOOD ?

47:36.830 --> 47:38.320
THAT'S INCREDIBLY
ORIGINAL.

47:38.330 --> 47:40.457
SHUT THE FUCK UP,
SCUMBAG !

47:40.460 --> 47:43.054
OH, LOOK, YOU GOT A CORPSE
IN THE FRONT SEAT.

47:43.060 --> 47:46.257
I SAID,
SHUT THE FUCK UP, SCUMBAG !

47:48.200 --> 47:49.428
GO!

47:49.430 --> 47:51.591
GO, GO, GO !

47:54.200 --> 47:56.088
IT'S OKAY.

47:56.100 --> 47:59.820
IT'S OKAY, IT'S OKAY,
JUST KEEP DRIVING.

48:07.630 --> 48:09.291
WHAT ARE YOU DOING ?

48:10.600 --> 48:11.794
WE HAVE TO GO BACK.

48:11.800 --> 48:13.199
ARE YOU INSANE ?

48:13.200 --> 48:14.952
WE HAVE TO GO BACK
AND MAKE SURE THAT GUY'S OKAY.

48:14.960 --> 48:16.393
I DIDN'T HIT HIM,
ALRIGHT ?

48:16.400 --> 48:17.992
HOW DO YOU KNOW,
I MEAN, ARE YOU SURE ?

48:18.000 --> 48:20.321
I SAW, HE'S FINE,
ALRIGHT ?

48:20.330 --> 48:22.423
THEN LET'S JUST GO BACK, AND
MAKE SURE THAT HE IS ALRIGHT !

48:22.430 --> 48:24.853
CLAIRE, I CANNOT
GO BACK THERE !

48:26.060 --> 48:28.119
GOD, I AM FUCKED !

48:28.130 --> 48:29.597
WELL, THIS IS JUST
MAKING IT WORSE !

48:29.600 --> 48:31.488
LISTEN TO ME.

48:31.500 --> 48:33.320
I NEED YOU TO JUST
HELP ME RIGHT NOW, OKAY ?

48:33.330 --> 48:34.649
PLEASE.

48:34.660 --> 48:37.424
I CAN'T HELP YOU !

48:37.430 --> 48:40.297
I CAN'T
HELP YOU ANYMORE !

48:40.300 --> 48:41.892
I CAN'T.

48:41.900 --> 48:44.323
LOOK, LET'S JUST
KEEP GOING, OKAY ?

48:44.330 --> 48:47.219
LET'S JUST KEEP GOING AND I WILL
FIGURE OUT WHAT TO DO, OKAY ?

48:47.230 --> 48:48.629
I WILL FIGURE IT OUT.

48:51.860 --> 48:53.657
I'M GOING BACK.

48:54.400 --> 48:55.822
GET OUT !

48:59.200 --> 49:00.827
CLAIRE, GIVE ME THAT.

49:00.830 --> 49:03.628
OKAY, YOU HAVE
TO GET OUT NOW.

49:03.630 --> 49:06.258
DON'T DO THIS TO ME.

49:06.260 --> 49:08.057
GET OUT !

49:09.960 --> 49:11.848
GET OUT !
OKAY !

49:11.860 --> 49:14.328
OKAY.

49:15.360 --> 49:17.692
I'M JUST GONNA
GET MY BAG, ALRIGHT ?

49:22.560 --> 49:24.528
THAN KS.

49:35.260 --> 49:37.091
OH, MY GOD.

50:20.860 --> 50:23.499
SO, WHERE DO YOU
THINK I AM, HMM ?

50:24.600 --> 50:26.397
HEAVEN OR HELL ?

50:26.400 --> 50:29.392
APPARENTLY, YOU'RE HERE,
AT THE MOMENT.

50:29.400 --> 50:31.857
YOU THINK I'M IN HELL.

50:33.000 --> 50:35.525
YEAH, SURE, I WENT TO CHURCH,
THAT WAS JUST FOR BUSINESS.

50:35.530 --> 50:37.259
I DIDN'T REALLY
BELIEVE IN GOD.

50:37.260 --> 50:40.024
I MEAN, NOT AS ANYONE
WHO YOU HAD TO PLEASE,

50:40.030 --> 50:41.622
OR IMPRESS,
TO GET "PROMOTED".

50:41.630 --> 50:46.124
NO, THE ONLY GOD I KNOW
IS A MEAN-SPIRITED COMEDIAN

50:46.130 --> 50:48.348
IN UGLY PANTS,

50:48.360 --> 50:51.227
WHOSE EVERY JOKE
HAS THE SAME DAMN PUNCH LINE.

50:51.230 --> 50:53.255
AND I'M THINKING
THAT KINDA ATTITUDE

50:53.260 --> 50:55.148
LANDS ME
STRAIGHT IN HELL.

50:55.160 --> 50:57.720
( laughing )

50:57.730 --> 50:59.425
ON THE BRIGHT SIDE,

50:59.430 --> 51:01.591
THAT MEANS...

51:01.600 --> 51:05.457
YOU'LL HAVE A FAMILIAR FACE
WAITING FOR YOU.

51:07.200 --> 51:09.998
HEY, LOOK IT UP.

51:10.000 --> 51:13.595
LEVITICUS,
CHAPTER 20, VERSE 13.

51:13.600 --> 51:16.319
I DON'T BELIEVE
THAT ANYMORE.

51:29.200 --> 51:31.498
AND I DON'T THINK
YOU'RE IN HELL.

51:32.930 --> 51:35.421
BUT YOU CAN'T QUITE SEE ME
HANGING AROUND WITH GANDHI

51:35.430 --> 51:37.227
AND MOTHER TERESA
UP THERE ?

51:39.560 --> 51:41.994
I MISS YOU, DAD.

51:45.360 --> 51:46.827
( Nate )
HEY.

51:48.400 --> 51:50.049
I THOUGHT YOU WERE
AT BRENDA'S.

51:50.060 --> 51:52.620
SHE HAD A LATE CLIENT,

51:52.630 --> 51:54.359
SO, I THOUGHT I'D,
YOU KNOW...

51:54.360 --> 51:56.726
HELP YOU CLEAN UP.

51:56.730 --> 51:57.924
THAN KS.

51:57.930 --> 52:00.524
AT THIS HOUR,
THAT IS A LATE CLIENT.

52:00.530 --> 52:03.499
SOME OF THEM LIKE HER
TO PUT THEM TO BED, YOU KNOW ?

52:03.500 --> 52:06.492
THAT'S VERY SAD.

52:06.500 --> 52:09.151
HEY, HOW LONG DID YOU
GO OUT WITH THAT COP ?

52:09.160 --> 52:11.628
ABOUT SIX MONTHS.

52:13.200 --> 52:15.122
SEX EVER SLOW DOWN ?

52:15.130 --> 52:17.758
I WAS SO HOPING YOU WEREN'T
GONNA GO THERE.

52:17.760 --> 52:20.524
( door opening and closing )
SORRY, FORGET IT.

52:22.260 --> 52:23.352
CLAIRE ?

52:23.360 --> 52:24.896
DAVID, I NEED SOME HELP.

52:24.900 --> 52:26.128
WHAT HAPPENED ?

52:26.130 --> 52:28.394
( sobbing )

52:32.030 --> 52:33.588
"FUCK MY LEGLESS
GRANDMOTHER !

52:33.600 --> 52:34.726
"AND FUCK YOU, ROBBIE,

52:34.730 --> 52:36.857
FOR NOT LETTING ME
HAVE A SNICKERS BAR !"

52:36.860 --> 52:38.521
OH, MY GOODNESS,
THE LANGUAGE !

52:38.530 --> 52:40.828
( laughing )

52:43.160 --> 52:44.923
I WAS SO RUDE.

52:44.930 --> 52:46.818
IT WAS FANTASTIC.

52:46.830 --> 52:48.627
QUELL BREAKTHROUGH.

52:48.630 --> 52:51.554
OH, ROBBIE, I DON'T EVEN
KNOW HOW TO THANK YOU.

52:51.560 --> 52:53.755
DON'T THANK ME.

52:55.260 --> 52:57.194
JUST CHANGE !

52:58.500 --> 53:00.559
SO, WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA DO TOMORROW

53:00.560 --> 53:02.755
TO START THE RENOVATIONS ?

53:02.760 --> 53:04.921
THAT'S NONE OF
YOUR FUCKING BUSINESS !

53:04.930 --> 53:07.922
( laughing )

53:17.630 --> 53:19.097
HI.

53:27.530 --> 53:29.794
ANY IDEA
WHERE HE'D GO ?

53:33.160 --> 53:35.196
WHAT WAS HE WEARING ?

53:39.530 --> 53:42.124
YOU KNOW, IT'S GONNA
BE MUCH EASIER ON HIM

53:42.130 --> 53:44.496
IF WE CAN BRING HIM IN
BEFORE SOMETHING ELSE HAPPENS.

53:44.500 --> 53:47.151
BUT HE DOESN'T
EVEN HAVE THE GUN...

53:47.160 --> 53:49.594
WHAT, YOU THINK HE CAN'T
GET ANOTHER GUN ?

53:52.400 --> 53:53.492
UM...

53:55.930 --> 53:59.149
HE WAS WEARING JEANS
AND A GREEN T-SHIRT, I THINK.

54:00.630 --> 54:02.222
YOU'RE DOING
THE RIGHT THING.

54:02.230 --> 54:04.391
YOU KNOW THAT,
RIGHT ?

54:06.560 --> 54:08.198
I FEEL LIKE SHIT.

54:08.200 --> 54:11.124
YOU'LL FEEL WORSE
IF SOMEONE ELSE GETS HURT.

54:12.830 --> 54:14.252
OH, MY GOD.

54:14.260 --> 54:17.923
WHEN THAT COP ASKED ME IF
I KNEW ABOUT THE 7-11 THING,

54:17.930 --> 54:19.397
I SAID I DIDN'T,
BUT I DID.

54:19.400 --> 54:22.096
IS THAT, LIKE,
REALLY BAD ?

54:22.100 --> 54:23.226
IT'S NOT GREAT.

54:23.230 --> 54:24.720
BUT YOU'RE TELLING
THE TRUTH NOW, RIGHT ?

54:24.730 --> 54:26.152
SO, DON'T WORRY
ABOUT THAT.

54:26.160 --> 54:28.628
YOU WOULDN'T MAKE ME,
LIKE, TESTIFY AGAINST HIM

54:28.630 --> 54:30.120
OR SOMETHING, RIGHT ?

54:30.130 --> 54:31.427
THAT'S NOT UP TO ME.

54:31.430 --> 54:33.591
BUT, ANYWAY,
THAT'S A LONG WAYS OFF.

54:33.600 --> 54:37.058
OKAY, 'CAUSE I DON'T WANT
TO DO ANYTHING LIKE THAT.

54:37.060 --> 54:39.449
GOD, WHY ARE YOU STILL
PROTECTING THIS LOSER ?

54:39.460 --> 54:41.257
BECAUSE SHE LOVES HIM.

54:44.860 --> 54:46.657
WE UNDERSTAND THAT,
CLAIRE.

54:46.660 --> 54:50.824
( David )
I REALLY WISH YOU'D TOLD us
ABOUT THIS SOON ER.

54:50.830 --> 54:52.821
HOW LONG DID YOU KNOW
ABOUT THE EMBALMING FLUID ?

54:52.830 --> 54:54.297
NOT THAT LONG.

54:54.300 --> 54:56.097
AND I TRIED
TO TELL NATE.

54:56.100 --> 54:58.398
WHEN, WHEN THE FUCK DID YOU
TRY AND TELL ME ABOUT THIS ?

54:58.400 --> 55:00.823
SHE'S TELLING YOU NOW,
ALRIGHT ?

55:01.130 --> 55:02.791
OKAY, I'M SORRY.

55:06.700 --> 55:08.452
I'M SORRY.

55:09.400 --> 55:10.992
WHEN YOU'RE READY,

55:11.000 --> 55:13.195
WE'RE GONNA GET IN THE CAR
AND DRIVE DOWN TO THE STATION,

55:13.200 --> 55:16.829
AND A COUPLE OF DETECT IVES
THERE ARE GONNA ASK YOU

55:16.830 --> 55:18.388
PRETTY MUCH
THE SAME QUESTIONS.

55:18.400 --> 55:21.096
WILL YOU BE THERE ?

55:21.100 --> 55:22.158
YES.

55:22.160 --> 55:23.889
I'LL BE THERE.

55:31.800 --> 55:34.394
( sobbing )

